deck: Monopoly Millionaire is an iOS game based on the Monopoly Millionaire board game.
description:
Overview

Monopoly Millionaire is a board game developed and published by Electronic Arts for the iPhone and iPad platforms.

Gameplay

Monopoly Millionaire takes the traditional Monopoly game and adds some twists and gameplay changes. In this version of Monopoly the goal is to be the first player to obtain one million dollars.

Monopoly Millionaire also adds two types of power up cards called lucky and fortune cards.

Multiplayer

Monopoly Millionaire supports two types of multiplayer, the first is a hot seat style pass and play and the other is over wifi.
name: Monopoly Millionaire

deck: Overwatch is a stylish, hero-based first-person multiplayer shooter created by Blizzard. A beta is set to launch in Fall 2015.
description:
Development History

Overwatch rises from the ashes of Titan, Blizzard's canceled MMO-project. Overwatch was the name of Titan's PVP component, featuring some of the same basic characters now found in Overwatch, albeit with different names. Overwatch uses the engine initially developed for Titan.
name: Overwatch
